# How to use this RAG based AI Teaching assistant on your own data

## Step 1 - Collect your data
Move your video files to the videos folder

## Step 2 - Convert to mp3
Convert all the video files to mp3 by running videos_to_mp3

## Step 3 - Convert mp3 to json
Convert all mp3 files to json by running mp3_to_json

## Step 4 - Convert json files to Vectors
Use the file preprocess_json to convert the json files to a dataframe with Embeddings and save it as a joblib pickle

## Step 5 - Prompt generation and feeding to LLM

In rag_engine Read the joblib file and load it into the memory. Then create a relevant prompt as per the user query and feed it to the LLM

## step 6 - create a website by using streamlit
In app.py create website for this so other can interect by name of sigma html AI tutor
